narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Port 110 is a great class and I would recommend it to another student. You learn a lot of Portuguese and culture.
I highly recommend this class! Portuguese is a hidden gem.
Portuguese is a great class! Not too much work, but I still felt like I had a decent grasp on the language by the end of the semester.

PORT 110 is a fabulous intro to a beautiful language. If you know Spanish or French, you will have a leg up for sure. The class will move quicker as a whole if everyone has had a second language already. I took it after already having fulfilled the language requirement and had a lot of fun! It will be what you make of it, with class every day, but don't miss out on learning about Brazilian culture on your own time too!
